alert.note: Alert for San Luis Obispo County Mountains; Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Watch issued March 13 at 3:06AM PDT until March 14 at 10:00PM PDT by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WATCH IN EFFECT FROM TUESDAY MORNING THROUGH TUESDAY EVENING... * WHAT...South winds 35 to 50 mph with gusts up to 60 mph possible. * WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Mountains and Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains. * WHEN...From Tuesday morning through Tuesday evening. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds could blow down large objects such as trees and power lines. Travel on area roadways could be affected, including Highway 166. Power outages are possible. Travel could be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: Monitor the latest forecasts and warnings for updates on this situation. Fasten loose objects or shelter objects in a safe location prior to the onset of winds.
